# .vscode/mcp.json was tracked until 2026-07-20 and had its portable `tilth`
# command replaced with a machine-local absolute path on every install, because
# install.sh runs `tilth install <host>` and tilth's installer writes the
# absolute binary path. That produced five separate "fix the path" commits
# (4751685, 43eebaa, 2495d6a, 1e9a92c, f408b4f) none of which addressed the
# cause. It is per-machine IDE config; the portable template is installed to
# ~/.config/token-diet/vscode-mcp.template.json instead.
.vscode/
dist/
excalidraw.log
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.p12
*.env.*

.token-budget
nul
.coverage
shipguard.txt

# Local tool artifacts (per-machine, never commit)
.gemini/
.hablatone
.ship-check-passed
.shipguard/

# Agent session working files. These accumulate machine-local absolute paths
# and read as session logs rather than project artifacts, so they stay out of
# the public tree. Keep them locally; never commit.
HANDOFF.md
